  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Assessment of myocardial ischemic-reperfusion injury during off- and on- pump CABG.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Assessment of myocardial ischemic-reperfusion injury during off- and on- pump CABG is
      monitored by intraoperative measurement of serum level of myeloperoxidase before sternotomy
      and after sternal closure.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
